This paper is primarily focused on object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the impact of different factors on the performance of object detectors, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses video data, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM), and discusses the spatial location accuracy, which is related to robotics (cs.RO).
